@baseUrl = http://localhost:38080
@adminUser = admin
@adminPass = change-me

### SPA 入口（前端已构建时应返回 200）
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin

?? status == 200 || status == 503

### 登录并建立 session
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUser}}",
  "password": "{{adminPass}}"
}

?? status == 200

### 查看当前会话
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/api/v1/auth/session

?? status == 200

### 退出登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/api/v1/auth/logout

?? status == 200
